// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0293 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 25397953-d7a1-59c4-b340-a8a3a5ee783e

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
